## Evaluating PDF Tool Privacy

### Red Flags

🚩 Requires account for basic features  
🚩 Uploads files to "cloud"  
🚩 Vague privacy policy  
🚩 Based in countries with weak privacy laws  
🚩 Shares data with "partners"  
